{"tid":2049337,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國示威感人一幕　白人警員有危險　非裔民眾「圍圈」保護","createTime":"2020-06-03T11:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T12:08:25.000Z","uid":213877,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a744a4f62115c6a19ce8ec58c3be7ee95de7b86d","tid":2049337,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200603/344831590939103232.jpeg/J_MpFqSuQ4eSh9n8HZgoCSnzys3-x5gcX_4I2V_-CNk?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200603%2F344831590939103232.jpeg%2FJ_MpFqSuQ4eSh9n8HZgoCSnzys3-x5gcX_4I2V_-CNk%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=faf3cb72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/世界說/481131/美國示威感人一幕-白人警員有危險-非裔民眾-圍圈-保護\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA%2F481131%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%84%9F%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%95-%E7%99%BD%E4%BA%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA-%E9%9D%9E%E8%A3%94%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE-%E5%9C%8D%E5%9C%88-%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BHdT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=6e7aa10b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/世界說/481131/美國示威感人一幕-白人警員有危險-非裔民眾-圍圈-保護</a><br />\n<br />\n美國明尼蘇達州非裔男子弗洛伊德（George Floyd）5月25日遭白人警方在執法時壓制頸部，導致無法呼吸後死亡。至此全美各地開始掀起「反警暴」、「反種族歧視」與「反執法過當」的連續抗爭，甚至出現多起示威群眾放火燒警局的事件，包括華盛頓在內的多個地區，也都實施宵禁或宣布緊急狀態。然而在這警民衝突之際，近日網路上則流傳一張黑人民眾保護白人警察的照片，由於該名警察在示威場合中落單，黑人民眾擔心他的安全，就手拉手的保護白人警察，讓不少網友看到後紛紛讚揚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據外媒Mamamia報道，該事件發生於5月28日晚間，肯塔基州（Kentucky）路易斯維爾正舉行一場抗議活動，其中一名白人警察不小心在街頭落單，結果被示威民眾逼到角落，沒想到下一秒多名黑人民眾紛紛手牽手，拉起人龍保護該名白人警察免受示威民眾攻擊，並且用肉身來保護他。<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200603/344806212119957504.jpeg/MUMF4LQA0NPJXoK3eSsmBmKrIkk1B7yG1-UM0tflDNI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200603%2F344806212119957504.jpeg%2FMUMF4LQA0NPJXoK3eSsmBmKrIkk1B7yG1-UM0tflDNI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=15f628dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n照片中可見，白人警察被逼到角落，一旁的示威民眾正作勢攻擊，所幸前方有一群黑人壯漢包圍保護，否則後果不堪設想。<br />\n<br />\n照片曝光後（編按：照片5月30日上載到Twitter），立刻在推特（Twitter）上瘋狂流傳，引來大批網友熱議，紛紛留言「當警察在攻擊，向手無寸鐵的和平示威者射擊橡皮子彈時，這名警察與他的隊員分開，這些『暴徒』保護了他，現在告訴我真正的暴徒是誰？」、「黑人也是人，Black lives matter」、「黑人跟一般人一樣，都很善良的」、「人道第一」、「希望不要再互相攻擊，而是互相保護彼此，每個人都是脆弱的族群」。"},{"pid":"21157d95eaa29af55af4d544826e767124bb4083","tid":2049337,"uid":77180,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:29:42.000Z","msg":"真和平示威者就要撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07852c7944ec45a5f445e6ebf426dc99c1963df5","tid":2049337,"uid":4526,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:32:06.000Z","msg":"-0-0"},{"pid":"67beed940b69e962c800c8b14a314da0e26dcc31","tid":2049337,"uid":103156,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:32:29.000Z","msg":"香港會告你非法禁錮"},{"pid":"be05892a9abada17910eb158d8b45155829cad89","tid":2049337,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:32:58.000Z","msg":"民主社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇異議<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aade4d68b02901132f6b63befc32b3f6ff45c1d3","tid":2049337,"uid":136797,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:33:03.000Z","msg":"左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d955182ad7a27efefaec92dd9b4d97e201b6384f","tid":2049337,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:35:48.000Z","msg":"個個都咁撚大隻"},{"pid":"db8cc2d2588fc11f58afeab93081fa8a9e9feb45","tid":2049337,"uid":73111,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:37:16.000Z","msg":"人地真係有白警<br />\n有腦有自己思想<br />